Description: Social volume shows the amount of daily project-related mentions on 1000+ crypto social media channels, including Telegram groups, crypto subreddits, Twitter and more.
Social dominance compares the social volume of an asset to the combined social volume of the 100 largest market cap assets.

Total social sentiment shows the average crowd sentiment about a specific project from 1000+ crypto social media channels, adjusted for the amount of unique project mentions daily. Positive values indicate the crowd sentiment is bullish on average, and vice versa.
